title: SwifTEA: Sure About Seashore
description:
It's time to catch up on some Taylor Swift theories! What is the Seashore theory? Are we finally going to finish off the trilogy? There's another Grammy win in the works! Are we a part of an exclusive club? And a very big heartfelt thanks for all of the love, listens and gifts.
What theories are you buying into? What did we miss? Lots of ways to contact us.. and we love hearing from you!
